Our homes reflect the values of our homebuyers and showcase our premium craftsmanship, service and commitment to unparalleled quality. Start looking for your brand new dream home in communities like San Mateo, Alameda, Solano, Santa Clara, Contra Costa, and San Joaquin counties. TRI Pointe Homes are also available in Southern California and Colorado.
 
