Life Inspiring HomesTM


TRI Pointe Group is a family of regional homebuilders built on a strong corporate foundation. Through our unique approach, we offer the best of big and small. Which means we have the large-scale resources and leadership of a national organization combined with the regional insights, community ties and agility of local home building companies. 


This allows us to create a new kind of model for the next generation of families. One that is inspired by the way people live and where they live. 


It’s an exciting opportunity to explore new ideas and advance the vision of homebuilding. And we’re just getting started.











